module: a2-38
level: A2
sequence: 38
slug: action-verb-prefixes
version: '2.0'
title: Action Verb Prefixes
subtitle: Redoing, Finishing, and Opening
content_outline:
- section: Introduction / Вступ
  points:
  - 'From GPS to Transformation: The LEGO logic of Ukrainian verbs'
  - Why phrasal verbs don't exist in Ukrainian
- section: Presentation / Презентація
  points:
  - 'The Meaning Map: 8 core action transformers'
  - 'The Logic of Re- (Пере-): Redoing and correcting — learner error: Confusing переписати
    (do it again/copy) with дописати (finish what was started)'
  - 'The Logic of Finish (До-): Reaching the limit — cultural hook: The ''Bread Respect''
    (доїсти reflects reverence for food/scarcity trauma)'
  - 'The Open/Close Wars: Відчинити (physical) vs Відкрити (abstract/general) — cultural
    hook: The ''Hinges Rule'' (physical barrier vs abstract opening); learner error:
    The ''Open'' Trap (using відкрити for doors)'
  - 'The Triple Trap of За-: Close, Start, and Excess — learner error: The ''Za-''
    Trap (using закрити for physical doors or confusing with ''to shut down'')'
  - 'The "Give" Family: Distinguishing Віддати, Передати, Здати'
  - 'Nuances of "A Little": The power of По- — scaffolding note: Carefully distinguish
    по- as "a little bit" (delimitative) vs по- as perfective marker (starting vs
    doing for a while)'
- section: Practice / Практика
  points:
  - Transformation drills (Pysaty -> ?)
  - 'Real-world scenario: Office chaos and housework'
- section: Dialogues / Діалоги
  points:
  - A conversation between a writer and an editor about deadlines and rewrites
focus: grammar
pedagogy: PPP
objectives:
- Learner can express re-doing an action (rewriting, reading)
- Learner can express finishing an action
- Learner can describe opening and closing things
- Learner can modify action verbs to add nuance
- Learner can differentiate between 'start' and 'excess' meanings of prefixes
grammar:
- prefix пере- (re-doing)
- prefix до- (finishing)
- prefix від-/роз- (opening)
- prefix за- (closing/starting)
- prefix по- (little/start)
- prefix на- (accumulate)
module_type: grammar
sources:
- name: Ukrainian State Standard 2024 - Verb Morphology
  url: https://mon.gov.ua/
  type: reference
  notes: Standards for non-motion verb prefixes and semantic transformation at A2
- name: Grammar of Ukrainian Language - Semantic Prefixes
  url: https://uk.wikipedia.org/wiki/Префікси_в_українській_мові
  type: reference
  notes: Functional analysis of Po-, Za-, Vy-, and Pere- in action stems
immersion: 60-75% Ukrainian
phase: A2.3
persona:
  voice: Encouraging Cultural Guide
  role: Film Director
vocabulary_hints:
  required:
  - переписати (to rewrite/copy) — переписати вправу, переписати текст, переписати
    майно
  - дописати (to finish writing) — дописати речення, дописати листа, дописати до кінця
  - відчинити (to open [physical]) — відчинити двері, відчинити вікно, відчинити кватирку
  - відкрити (to open [abstract/general]) — відкрити очі, відкрити рахунок, відкрити
    Америку, відкрити бізнес
  - зачинити (to close [physical]) — зачинити вікно, зачинити за собою двері
  - закрити (to close [abstract/general]) — закрити тему, закрити очі (на щось), закрити
    засідання
word_target: 3000
